# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Teacher Copilot — environment configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and add your OpenRouter API key.
#
# WITHOUT a key, the app still runs in DEMO MODE with realistic
# pre-written content — perfect for a safe live demo.
# WITH a key, all features use real AI generation via OpenRouter.
# Get a free key at https://openrouter.ai/keys

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model (default: anthropic/claude-opus-4-8)
# Any model available on openrouter.ai works:
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=openai/gpt-4o
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=google/gemini-2.5-pro
